title: Black Milk x BADBADNOTGOOD – “Now or Never” (OFFICIAL AUDIO STREAM)
description:
“Now or Never” is the second single off of the second Converse CONS compilation, CONS EP Vol. 2, coming later this fall. The song was partially recorded at Converse Rubber Tracks in Brooklyn, New York. 

Produced by: Black Milk & BADBADNOTGOOD 
Music by: BADBADNOTGOOD
Lyrics by: Black Milk
Vocals by: Black Milk
